  "Name": {
    "English": "TEAL RIBBON FIREWORK",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "蓝绿丝带烟花",
    "TraditionalChinese": "青絲帶煙火"
  },
  "NameLower": {
    "English": "Teal Ribbon Firework",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "蓝绿丝带烟花",
    "TraditionalChinese": "青絲帶煙火"
  },
  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Consumable Pyrotechnics Device",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "消耗型烟火技术设备",
    "TencentChinese": "消耗型烟火技术设备",
    "TraditionalChinese": "消耗型煙火表演裝置"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "This exotic firework, sparkling with <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">zinc</span> and <VAL_ON>antimony<> elements, bursts into a cluster of wildly spiralling ribbons. Ignite to create glittering displays in the sky.<br><br>Place launch tube via the <VAL_ON>Build Menu<> (<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>). <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning</span>: Aim away from living creatures. Not recommended for indoor use.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这枚不同寻常的烟花中加入了<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">锌</span>与<VAL_ON>锑<>元素，击发后会炸出一簇扭结缠绕的丝带。点燃后在天空中开启一场炫丽的光影表演。<br><br>可以通过<VAL_ON>建造菜单<>（<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>）来放置发射筒。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：不可瞄准活体生物。不建议在室内使用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這種充滿異國風情的煙火會綻放為成簇狂亂旋轉的絲帶，並帶有<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">鋅</span>與<VAL_ON>銻<>元素的光輝。點燃即可在天空中創造出絢爛效果。<br><br>從<VAL_ON>建造選單<> (<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>) 放置發射管。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：請勿對著生物發射，不建議於室內使用。"
  },
